// =============================================================================
// MOVE DATABASE — Cascadia
// =============================================================================
// Comprehensive Pokemon move data, Gen 1-9 vanilla statlines used as foundation.
// Source: Bulbapedia (cross-referenced). Each move animation is hosted by the
// Reborn-derived Gen 9 Move Animation Project loaded from /assets/animations/.
//
// Schema:
//   name:        Display name
//   type:        Type id (matches typeChart.js)
//   category:    'physical' | 'special' | 'status'
//   power:       Base power (0 for status)
//   accuracy:    0-100; 0 means always hits
//   pp:          Max PP
//   priority:    -7 to +5 (default 0; omitted when 0)
//   flags:       Tags ('contact', 'punch', 'sound', 'pulse', 'biting', 'kicking',
//                 'wind', 'slicing', 'powder', 'ballistic', 'recharge')
//   effect:      Optional secondary effect
//   critRate:    Extra crit stage (default 0)
//   drain:       Fraction of damage healed (e.g. 0.5)
//   recoil:      Fraction of damage taken back (e.g. 0.25)
//   description: Brief flavor text
//
// Moves marked with `// VERIFY` indicate stats that may have changed across
// generations or that I'm slightly less certain of and should be audited
// before serious balancing.
// =============================================================================

